### Criar uma Ordem de Pedido (Coca Cola 2L)
POST http://localhost:3000/product-orders HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "barcode": "123412112",
  "orderQuantity": 10,
  "orderDate": "2026-05-15T14:30:00Z"
}

